Move.ConsentToCounterAction:
He disguised himself as a very old man, so that he would be unrecognizable, came to the palace, and said to the king:
"Your Majesty, hire me as your herdsman."
"Very well," said the king, "be my herdsman.
When the three-headed dragon comes to your herd, give him three cows;
when the six-headed dragon comes, give him six cows;
and when the twelve-headed dragon comes, count off twelve cows."
